Developer Terms of Use
des: This skill provides the ability to remotely start your Transcend Smart Sauna. To set up, simply say "Set Up My Sauna," followed by your sauna ID which can be found in your sauna's utilities screen under "REMOTE APP." After a successful setup, you can start your sauna by saying "start my sauna." This will begin the warmup process. You can also start warmup for a specific user by saying, "start warmup for user 2."
